Assignment 1 â€“ HPC SOFTWARE

Compilation
-----------
Load modules:

module purge
module load mpi/latest

Compile using make:

make


Programs
--------

Q1 Send/Recv version
mpirun -np 4 ./q1_sendrecv input16.txt
mpirun -np 10 ./q1_sendrecv input10000.txt


Q1 Collective version
mpirun -np 4 ./q1_collective input16.txt
mpirun -np 10 ./q1_collective input10000.txt


Q2 Decomposition
mpirun -np 9 ./q2_test 25
mpirun -np 10 ./q2_test 100000
mpirun -np 1 ./q2_test 25


Q3 Norm computation
mpirun -np 4 ./q3_norm q3file_16.txt
mpirun -np 11 ./q3_norm q3file_97.txt
mpirun -np 6 ./q3_norm q3file_97.txt
mpirun -np 1 ./q3_norm q3file_16.txt


Cleaning executables
--------------------
make clean

